---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<section id="course" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-charcoal">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-accent-yellow">Course Highlights</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
        <Icon name="mdi:image-edit" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent-green mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent-orange">Meme Formats Mastery</h3>
        <p>Learn the anatomy of viral memes and master classic and emerging formats.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
        <Icon name="mdi:trending-up" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent-green mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent-orange">Trend Surfing</h3>
        <p>Develop a sixth sense for spotting and riding the waves of viral trends.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
        <Icon name="mdi:palette" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent-green mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent-orange">Meme Aesthetics</h3>
        <p>Master the art of visual humor with expert design and editing techniques.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
        <Icon name="mdi:account-group" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent-green mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent-orange">Community Building</h3>
        <p>Learn to create and nurture a loyal following for your meme content.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
        <Icon name="mdi:brain" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent-green mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent-orange">Meme Psychology</h3>
        <p>Understand what makes content shareable and how to trigger viral responses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 transform hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">
        <Icon name="mdi:rocket-launch" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent-green mb-4" />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent-orange">Meme Marketing</h3>
        <p>Harness the power of memes for brand building and digital marketing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>